  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ……ここんとこ、
お魚使った料理が続いてるよね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah...To think that we'd still be cooking with fish
up til now...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ、魚好き！
肉も好きだけど！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well I like fish! I like meat too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;は野菜も食べなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eat vegetables as well, &lt;Dio&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;さんは、
お魚、嫌いなんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you not like fish, &lt;Rody&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>食べるのはいいけど……
料理するのが、ちょっとね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well I'm fine with eating them, however
cooking them are a bit....y'know...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42900</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>目がダメなんだよね、
あのじっとこっちを見てる感じ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's their eyes...Those fishes are always staring at
me whenever I prepare them...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、&lt;Rody&gt;さん、
お魚さばく時、目隠ししてるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ohh, so that's why you always cover your eyes when
preparing them...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>need context</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すげー！　&lt;Rody&gt;、目隠しして
包丁使えるのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa that's so cool! You can use a knife
while blindfolded?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すごいっていうか……
危ない気が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel that "dangerous" is a more apt descriptor
for this situation...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_183_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや、目隠しするのは
お魚さんの方だよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, no, I think the fish 
should be blindfolded instead.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
